cu.explanation_en: Setting Asn1_verbosity to an invalid enum value 'invalid' will cause configuration parsing errors and prevent the CU from starting properly.

du.explanation_en: Setting do_CSIRS to an out-of-range value 2 (valid values are 0 or 1) will cause configuration validation errors and prevent the DU from initializing correctly.
du.explanation_zh: 將 do_CSIRS 設定為超出範圍的值 2（有效值為 0 或 1）會導致配置驗證錯誤，並阻止 DU 正確初始化。
